data.description: Sophisticated one floor living nestled in sought after York County! Many upgrades enhance this remodeled 4 bedroom, 3 bath 2346 Sq Ft home. Well thought-out floor plan with open living room-kitchen enhance your modern lifestyle. This spacious room with a gas fireplace, loads of natural light, neutral paint and so much more to enjoy. Stainless steel appliances, laminate counters, tile backsplash, pantry and extra large eat-in bar area to upgrade your culinary experience. Enjoy the morning room with an abundance of natural light and walk out porch. Encase yourself in comfort and luxury in the Master suite.  Large deck offers the entertaining space you will love. Large yard with fenced in backyard and circular drive makes entering and leaving this home a true gem!
